13:07.187 --> 13:11.956
â™ª I can see
for miles and miles â™ª

13:11.958 --> 13:15.226
â™ª and miles...

13:15.228 --> 13:17.796
â™ª oh, yeah.

13:31.043 --> 13:35.046
Ryan:
<i>All my patients' files</i>
<i>were stolen from my computer</i>

13:35.048 --> 13:37.448
<i>And all their secrets</i>
<i>made public.</i>

13:37.450 --> 13:39.450
Nelson:
<i>So did you catch him?</i>
<i>The hacker?</i>

13:39.452 --> 13:41.452
Ryan:
<i>Still don't even know</i>
<i>who he is.</i>

13:41.454 --> 13:44.556
Our target's trying
to get my attention.

13:44.558 --> 13:47.826
Wait, exposing secrets
and embarrassing people is a way

13:47.828 --> 13:51.196
You have no personal connection
to any of the victims.

13:53.265 --> 13:54.899
You have a personal connection
to the target.

13:54.901 --> 13:56.434
It's a reminder of...

13:56.436 --> 13:59.037
New york when he stole
all my patient files.

13:59.039 --> 14:00.038
So why now?

14:00.040 --> 14:01.439
Why not three months from now?

14:01.441 --> 14:03.575
Because nelson
stirred the monster.

14:03.577 --> 14:06.110
And he thought nelson was you.

14:06.112 --> 14:08.513
He thought you'd discovered him,
and he got scared.

14:08.515 --> 14:10.181
Yeah, but it didn't scare him.

14:10.183 --> 14:12.851
It thrilled him.
This is part of his endgame.

14:12.853 --> 14:15.854
Nelson didn't just find
my old patient files.

14:15.856 --> 14:18.456
He discovered I'm being watched

14:18.458 --> 14:22.193
And I have been since the day
my practice was hacked.

14:22.195 --> 14:23.895
What?

14:23.897 --> 14:26.965
I was always my hacker's
intended victim.

14:28.200 --> 14:30.869
So your fingerprint
on that hourglass

14:30.871 --> 14:33.538
At dr. Chan's murder scene,
that was his message,

14:33.540 --> 14:36.207
His way of guaranteeing
you'd be involved.

14:36.209 --> 14:39.210
Our target has been lying
in wait

14:39.212 --> 14:42.013
Preparing for this day.

14:44.383 --> 14:47.452
All right. That's
every computer I owned

14:47.454 --> 14:49.420
Since I was first hacked.

14:49.422 --> 14:51.089
So this is your place, huh?

14:51.091 --> 14:53.892
Nice. Homey.

14:53.894 --> 14:56.027
Well, what did you expect?

14:56.029 --> 14:57.629
Oh, I don't know.

14:57.631 --> 15:00.498
A drum set, velvet elvis,

15:00.500 --> 15:02.066
Pet alligator.

15:02.068 --> 15:03.534
Well, he's at the vet.

15:05.638 --> 15:09.908
Any-who, um,
I brought you a present.

15:11.210 --> 15:13.511
Couldn't leave you
without a computer or a phone,

15:13.513 --> 15:15.179
So...

15:16.348 --> 15:18.216
Fbi laptop. Clean as a whistle.

15:18.218 --> 15:20.585
Connected to
our network.

15:20.587 --> 15:23.554
And... Burner cell.

15:23.556 --> 15:25.423
With all your contacts
already uploaded.

15:25.425 --> 15:27.125
Thanks, krummy.

15:32.064 --> 15:34.165
If you want, I could stay.

15:34.167 --> 15:37.101
Aw.
I have a new
binary code app.

15:37.103 --> 15:39.437
Anyway, um,
so your-your security detail

15:39.439 --> 15:41.406
Is, uh, parked outside

15:41.408 --> 15:44.609
And, uh, I will see you
in the morning, boss.

15:44.611 --> 15:46.244
(chuckles)

15:46.246 --> 15:48.313
(chuckling):
Oh. Thank you, daniel.

15:58.557 --> 16:00.358
So...

16:00.360 --> 16:04.595
<i>She transferred the video file</i>
<i>with the embedded rat.</i>

16:07.299 --> 16:09.500
With every transfer, she was
basically rat'ing herself.

16:09.502 --> 16:12.303
Ramirez:
When she clicked on the infected
video file on her new computer,

16:12.305 --> 16:13.972
The hacker had complete control.

16:13.974 --> 16:15.606
So to find the hacker,

16:15.608 --> 16:17.275
We need to find
the legacy device.

16:17.277 --> 16:20.111
The very first computer the
hacker infected with the rat.

16:20.113 --> 16:21.579
The one he
actually touched.

16:21.581 --> 16:23.648
The only one that can
lead us to him.

16:23.650 --> 16:25.283
Our digital patient zero.

16:25.285 --> 16:27.085
Sounds great, but it's not here.

16:27.087 --> 16:29.554
But we do have
dr. Chan's laptop.

16:29.556 --> 16:31.689
Which was infected directly
by the hacker.

16:31.691 --> 16:33.558
That's where we'll start.

16:33.560 --> 16:35.626
Aw, you're so smart.

16:35.628 --> 16:37.695
(scoffs)
don't even try it.

16:37.697 --> 16:40.365
What?
I'm still mad
at you.

16:40.367 --> 16:42.367
Sifter. What?

16:42.369 --> 16:45.436
What about daniel krumitz?

16:46.705 --> 16:48.706
Is everything okay?

16:48.708 --> 16:51.509
No, it is not.

16:51.511 --> 16:54.379
Taylor pettis filed a report
with metro pd.

16:54.381 --> 16:56.047
Claims you threatened him.

16:57.549 --> 17:00.151
(sighs) you know, daniel,
this is serious.

17:00.153 --> 17:03.588
Your badge doesn't give you
authority to break the law.

17:03.590 --> 17:05.056
I didn't break the law.

17:05.058 --> 17:08.793
And unless you're gonna suspend
me or assign me to desk duty

17:08.795 --> 17:11.496
And put me on probation, I don't
really want to talk about it.

17:11.498 --> 17:12.563
Hey. Sit down.

17:14.466 --> 17:16.567
We're not done yet.

17:17.636 --> 17:19.637
My friend,
you are trapped in ice.

17:19.639 --> 17:22.407
When a traumatic event happens
to us at a certain age,

17:22.409 --> 17:26.411
We tend to always relate to it
like we're still that same age.

17:26.413 --> 17:28.413
Okay, so I'll just grow up.

17:28.415 --> 17:31.749
You see, right there, that was
the frustrated, scared response

17:31.751 --> 17:33.818
Of a ten-year-old.

17:38.223 --> 17:42.393
I watched my best friend
burn to death.

17:42.395 --> 17:44.829
In college, we were
driving back to campus

17:44.831 --> 17:47.398
After thanksgiving break.

17:47.400 --> 17:50.134
A truck driver fell asleep
at the wheel,

17:50.136 --> 17:51.302
Slammed right into us.

17:51.304 --> 17:54.539
Brian whispered his last words
into my ear.

17:56.308 --> 17:59.544
Since then,
every whisper I hear,

17:59.546 --> 18:01.112
Somebody
leans forward

18:01.114 --> 18:03.114
To share a
confidence with me,

18:03.116 --> 18:05.483
I don't even hear the words.

18:05.485 --> 18:07.518
Just his whisper.

18:07.520 --> 18:09.854
"don't let me die."

18:10.823 --> 18:13.691
You're never gonna get rid
of the loss,

18:13.693 --> 18:16.727
But you have got to get past
this anger. Because that...

18:16.729 --> 18:19.530
Ten-year-old kid
who lost his parents

18:19.532 --> 18:23.468
Is now a 28-year-old man.

18:38.717 --> 18:40.818
(sighs)

18:56.535 --> 18:59.537
(alarm beeping)

19:01.306 --> 19:04.575
Krumitz, what's going on?

19:04.577 --> 19:06.644
I don't know. It's happening
in tear down, too.

19:06.646 --> 19:08.212
Excuse me.

19:08.214 --> 19:10.515
One of our computers was
infected with a malicious code.

19:11.617 --> 19:12.617
Cyber's been hacked?

19:12.619 --> 19:14.185
Looks like the same rat

19:14.187 --> 19:15.887
We found on dr. Chan
and avery's computers.

19:18.223 --> 19:20.591
Ryan:
All right,
you want to play games?

19:21.693 --> 19:23.895
Let's play.

19:27.266 --> 19:29.333
(crying softly)

19:40.412 --> 19:41.679
Mundo:
How did this happen?

19:41.681 --> 19:43.281
Did we infect ourselves?
Krumitz: No.

19:43.283 --> 19:45.249
It looks
like avery infected herself.

19:45.251 --> 19:46.517
I thought
you took all her devices.

19:46.519 --> 19:48.186
I gave her an fbi laptop.

19:48.188 --> 19:49.921
But she needed the video file
on the flash drive.

19:51.523 --> 19:53.457
Wait a minute.
It's gone.

19:53.459 --> 19:54.559
What?

19:54.561 --> 19:56.627
The flash drive.
I-I put it right here.

19:56.629 --> 19:57.562
She doesn't want us to know
what she's doing.

20:05.370 --> 20:07.371
I know you hacked my computer.

20:07.373 --> 20:10.274
I know you're watching me.

20:10.276 --> 20:12.677
You have my attention.
What do you want now?

20:33.799 --> 20:35.700
(alarm continues beeping)

20:35.702 --> 20:37.235
(groans)

20:37.237 --> 20:39.604
(vibrating)

20:40.572 --> 20:43.975
Come on. Pick up, pick up.

20:51.650 --> 20:53.451
Man (over speaker):
Good morning,
ladies and gentlemen.

20:53.453 --> 20:56.787
The 5:30 departure for richmond
is now boarding.

21:13.705 --> 21:15.773
(beeping)

21:28.720 --> 21:30.688
(phone chiming)

21:34.593 --> 21:37.361
It's glued down. Smart.

22:00.952 --> 22:02.453
(phone chimes)

22:12.597 --> 22:14.398
Mundo: <i>Krumitz worked through</i>
<i>the night eradicating the virus</i>

22:14.400 --> 22:16.033
<i>From ctoc.</i>
<i>Sifter:</i> <i>That's great, but</i>

22:16.035 --> 22:18.035
Our target's just
released information

22:18.037 --> 22:20.338
On three more
of dr. Chan's patients.

22:20.340 --> 22:21.839
Any word from avery?
No.

22:21.841 --> 22:23.774
And we can't track her.
Avery's gone dark.

22:23.776 --> 22:25.476
What do you think?

22:25.478 --> 22:26.777
I think this is personal.

22:26.779 --> 22:27.978
I think avery went after
her hacker.

22:27.980 --> 22:29.847
We got something
off of dr. Chan's laptop.

22:29.849 --> 22:32.717
The hacker was clever.
He was hopping his I.P. Address.

22:32.719 --> 22:34.518
We finally found the network
the rat was using

22:34.520 --> 22:37.822
We also got a physical
address on him as well.

22:37.824 --> 22:39.790
We know exactly
where our hacker is.

22:51.002 --> 22:52.770
Don't shoot,
don't shoot,

22:52.772 --> 22:54.572
Don't shoot,
don't shoot.
Hands up. On the floor.

22:54.574 --> 22:56.507
On the floor now.
Okay. I'm down,
I'm down.

22:56.509 --> 22:57.942
Clear.

22:57.944 --> 22:59.543
(grunts)

22:59.545 --> 23:00.678
What is this about?

23:00.680 --> 23:03.748
Swat officer:
Clear.
Ow.

23:03.750 --> 23:05.883
What is this about?

23:06.752 --> 23:08.786
Where's avery?
Avery?

23:08.788 --> 23:10.488
Where is she?!
Avery ryan?

23:10.490 --> 23:12.823
Wh... Aah!

23:12.825 --> 23:13.958
Your code was old-school,
andrew.

23:13.960 --> 23:15.826
It was tough to break,
but we got you.

23:15.828 --> 23:16.927
So one more time.

23:16.929 --> 23:18.529
Aah!
Where is she?

23:18.531 --> 23:20.631
I don't know what's happened,
but I swear to you

23:20.633 --> 23:22.533
I haven't seen
my ex-wife in years.

23:24.002 --> 23:25.636
What'd you say?

23:27.639 --> 23:30.775
I last saw avery
four years ago in new york.

23:30.777 --> 23:33.511
I haven't seen
my ex-wife since then.

23:46.691 --> 23:48.759
(clang, whoosh)

24:14.653 --> 24:16.554
Not bad.

24:16.556 --> 24:19.924
You worked hard
to set all this up.

24:19.926 --> 24:22.059
I'm almost impressed.

24:29.067 --> 24:31.669
Well, you have
a pretty impressive

24:31.671 --> 24:33.737
Eye for detail.

24:35.941 --> 24:37.975
You were one of my patients.

24:37.977 --> 24:40.911
(laughs)
oh.

24:40.913 --> 24:43.814
You stole this.

24:43.816 --> 24:45.616
Mmm.

24:46.785 --> 24:48.152
And my hourglass

24:48.154 --> 24:50.087
And my patient files.

24:50.089 --> 24:52.490
You ruined my practice.

24:52.492 --> 24:54.758
My only question is why.

24:54.760 --> 24:57.828
You went to all this trouble

24:57.830 --> 25:00.130
To re-create my office

25:00.132 --> 25:03.834
To get me to come here,
so where are you?

25:03.836 --> 25:05.803
Man:
You failed.

25:05.805 --> 25:08.105
You failed all your patients.

25:19.885 --> 25:21.752
You knew avery was married,

25:21.754 --> 25:23.187
And you never
said anything?

25:23.189 --> 25:25.956
I don't share
avery's background with anyone.

25:25.958 --> 25:28.192
Or yours, for that matter.

25:28.194 --> 25:30.528
Will somebody
please tell me

25:30.530 --> 25:31.929
What's going on here?

25:31.931 --> 25:34.098
We are trying
to find avery, sir.

25:34.100 --> 25:35.966
That's why your people
are searching my house

25:35.968 --> 25:37.868
And snooping
through my computer?
All we know

25:37.870 --> 25:40.004
Is that somebody's computer
got hacked in just the same way

25:40.006 --> 25:42.640
That your ex-wife's
got hacked ten years ago.

25:42.642 --> 25:44.909
And our investigation, sir,

25:44.911 --> 25:46.944
Has led us right to you.

25:46.946 --> 25:48.546
Well, let me
assure you that

25:48.548 --> 25:50.881
I would never do anything
to hurt avery.

25:50.883 --> 25:52.216
Mundo:
Divorce is tough.

25:52.218 --> 25:53.784
I've been there.

25:53.786 --> 25:55.085
Resentment builds.

25:55.087 --> 25:56.253
Anger.

25:56.255 --> 25:57.888
Sounds like
you have a lot of issues.

25:57.890 --> 25:59.890
None of which I can relate to.

25:59.892 --> 26:01.959
What came between avery and I...

26:04.863 --> 26:06.864
Do I need a lawyer?

26:06.866 --> 26:08.999
Tell me, how did I fail you?

26:09.001 --> 26:12.136
You were quite fond
of your other patients.

26:12.138 --> 26:13.737
My other patients.

26:13.739 --> 26:14.738
But not you?

26:14.740 --> 26:16.340
No. We were close.

26:16.342 --> 26:19.176
Close. You felt
we had something more.

26:19.178 --> 26:21.579
We had something special.

26:21.581 --> 26:24.615
Well, something must have
happened in our relationship.

26:25.717 --> 26:28.619
You hacked my computer
and stole my files.

26:28.621 --> 26:30.921
Demonstrating
how powerful you were.

26:30.923 --> 26:34.191
How powerful I am.

26:34.193 --> 26:37.194
(chuckles) of course.

26:37.196 --> 26:38.829
Well, if you brought me here

26:38.831 --> 26:40.898
For a session,
maybe we should start

26:40.900 --> 26:44.201
With your delusional fantasies
and your obsessive behavior.

26:44.203 --> 26:48.973
Dr. Ryan, you've been after me
for a very long time.

26:48.975 --> 26:50.674
It keeps you up at night.

26:50.676 --> 26:52.676
You came here today
looking for answers,

26:52.678 --> 26:55.079
Despite the possible danger.

26:55.081 --> 26:57.982
So you tell me,
who's delusional and obsessive?

27:03.321 --> 27:04.822
His computer's squeaky clean.

27:04.824 --> 27:06.624
He didn't hack
dr. Chan or avery.

27:06.626 --> 27:07.958
All right, well, someone's
working awfully hard

27:07.960 --> 27:09.226
To put hubby in
our crosshairs.

27:09.228 --> 27:10.961
Sifter:
I know it was
a while ago,

27:10.963 --> 27:12.963
But is there anything
in particular you recall

27:12.965 --> 27:14.965
About that time that
avery's files were hacked?

27:14.967 --> 27:17.368
Well, we were divorced by then.

27:17.370 --> 27:19.003
Next time we spoke,
she dropped by here,

27:19.005 --> 27:20.838
Told me she was
moving to d.C.,

27:20.840 --> 27:24.041
Asked me to hold on
to some of her old office stuff

27:24.043 --> 27:26.243
Until she sent for it.
Which she never did.

27:26.245 --> 27:27.978
Office stuff?

27:27.980 --> 27:29.113
Yeah, books, pictures,

27:29.115 --> 27:32.149
Files, an old
computer-- stuff.

27:34.953 --> 27:37.221
I was hoping we'd be able
to speak in person.

27:37.223 --> 27:39.857
I prefer to speak this way.

27:39.859 --> 27:43.761
There are 77 files
on the screen,

27:43.763 --> 27:47.131
Displaying each patient's
last name.

27:47.133 --> 27:51.135
I had 78 patients.

27:51.137 --> 27:54.138
You're conspicuous
by your absence.

27:54.140 --> 27:56.306
I should've known it was you

27:56.308 --> 27:59.209
When I walked into an abandoned
steel factory.

27:59.211 --> 28:01.812
Your abusive father
was a steelworker.

28:01.814 --> 28:04.014
You told me what he did to you.

28:04.016 --> 28:05.115
It's because of him

28:05.117 --> 28:08.185
You have such severe
social anxiety.

28:10.855 --> 28:13.857
It's what keeps you
on that side of the screen...

28:13.859 --> 28:17.027
Logan.

28:17.029 --> 28:19.063
Logan reeves.

28:21.366 --> 28:22.966
(door squeaks open)

28:51.730 --> 28:54.798
Why don't you have a seat,
logan, so we can get started?

28:54.800 --> 28:56.400
I'll stand.

28:56.402 --> 29:00.070
Whatever makes you
most comfortable.

29:04.342 --> 29:06.944
Let's talk about
how you're feeling.

29:06.946 --> 29:08.445
Clearly you're still
angry with your father,

29:08.447 --> 29:11.949
Which is why you chose
this place for our session.

29:11.951 --> 29:14.451
This is not about him.

29:14.453 --> 29:16.453
What is it about, then?

29:16.455 --> 29:18.388
You promised me that
you'd always be there.

29:18.390 --> 29:19.890
That you'd help.

29:19.892 --> 29:23.127
Well, I'm sorry
you feel that I failed you.

29:23.129 --> 29:26.497
You need to understand
I could no longer help you.

29:26.499 --> 29:28.132
You abandoned me.

29:28.134 --> 29:30.501
You pushed me off
onto another doctor

29:30.503 --> 29:33.203
Who forced me
into taking medications

29:33.205 --> 29:35.305
That only made things worse.
Logan,

29:35.307 --> 29:38.342
You suffer
from a delusional disorder.

29:38.344 --> 29:42.813
You needed further treatment
which I could not provide.

29:42.815 --> 29:44.982
That's not true.

29:44.984 --> 29:46.950
I read your notes.

29:48.086 --> 29:51.488
(scoffs) "patient
responding to treatment."

29:51.490 --> 29:53.490
Responding.

29:53.492 --> 29:55.092
I was improving.

29:55.094 --> 29:56.927
That was before I understood

29:56.929 --> 29:59.863
Your attachment to me
was hindering your progress.

30:01.166 --> 30:04.434
You were the only person
that could ever help me.

30:04.436 --> 30:07.137
Well, I'm here now.

30:07.139 --> 30:09.840
Let's talk.

30:20.819 --> 30:23.453
Here's the laptop avery's
ex-husband gave us.

30:23.455 --> 30:25.923
The legacy device.
The rat's been
on this computer for years.

30:25.925 --> 30:27.291
Avery had no way of knowing.

30:27.293 --> 30:29.827
But the hacker had to leave
digital fingerprints.

30:29.829 --> 30:32.863
Krummy, pull up the event log
with all the connected devices.

30:32.865 --> 30:34.464
That computer connected
to a couple dozen

30:34.466 --> 30:36.133
External devices
throughout its life.

30:36.135 --> 30:38.135
Krumitz:
Yeah, we're looking
for the outlier.

30:38.137 --> 30:40.237
Uh...
Nelson: There.

30:40.239 --> 30:42.573
The devices on this list
have connected multiple times,

30:42.575 --> 30:45.542
Ramirez:
Only plugged in once.
Nelson: That's our rat.

30:45.544 --> 30:48.178
It's got to be.
How did
the hacker

30:48.180 --> 30:50.047
Gain access to avery's
laptop in the first place?

30:50.049 --> 30:54.885
The transfer occurred
on a Wednesday at 2:34 p.M.

30:54.887 --> 30:56.854
Business hours.
A patient.

30:56.856 --> 30:58.222
Okay, we've got
avery's old

30:58.224 --> 31:00.390
Address book on here.
On that date and time...

31:00.392 --> 31:01.925
Uh, she was in a session.

31:01.927 --> 31:05.596
"patient exhibits paranoid
and delusional tendencies.

31:05.598 --> 31:07.931
"anxiety. Anger.

31:07.933 --> 31:10.467
"potential early onset
psychotic disorder.

31:10.469 --> 31:12.636
Not a danger to himself
or others at this time."

31:12.638 --> 31:16.073
That's reassuring.
Not so fast.

31:16.075 --> 31:17.941
According to
the fbi database,

31:17.943 --> 31:19.576
Over the last decade,
logan reeves

31:19.578 --> 31:20.978
Has been arrested
multiple times.

31:20.980 --> 31:23.981
All violent
charges.

31:23.983 --> 31:25.582
Avery:
<i>Tell me about when you first</i>

31:25.584 --> 31:29.019
As I recall, you didn't
even like computers.

31:29.021 --> 31:31.922
Mmm. (softly laughs)

31:31.924 --> 31:33.490
I liked you.

31:35.627 --> 31:38.295
I became a proficient hacker
to get to know you better.

31:38.297 --> 31:41.632
I... Felt like you knew
everything about me.

31:41.634 --> 31:43.500
I knew nothing about you.

31:43.502 --> 31:45.669
It was a very
one-sided relationship.

31:45.671 --> 31:49.673
Mmm. Well, that's
what therapy is.

31:49.675 --> 31:52.910
I was your doctor,
not your friend.

31:52.912 --> 31:54.645
For someone who claims
to be so perceptive,

31:54.647 --> 31:57.648
You clearly don't understand
what this is all about.

31:57.650 --> 31:58.115
Then tell me.

32:02.654 --> 32:05.355
It's not about
you fixing me, okay?

32:07.025 --> 32:08.458
See, you...

32:08.460 --> 32:12.095
Had your chance to help me.

32:12.097 --> 32:14.364
But you gave up!

32:14.366 --> 32:17.000
You gave up on me!

32:25.443 --> 32:27.711
We need a lock on this guy asap.

32:27.713 --> 32:30.013
Last knowns. Current aliases.

32:30.015 --> 32:34.051
I want to know everything
there is about logan reeves.

32:34.053 --> 32:36.086
I got logan's
last known address.

32:36.088 --> 32:38.588
Saratoga springs.
Mental institution.

32:38.590 --> 32:41.024
Unfortunately, it closed down
a little over a year ago.

32:41.026 --> 32:44.661
Back out on the street.
No follow-ups. No clue.

32:44.663 --> 32:46.163
You've got to be kidding me.

32:46.165 --> 32:49.266
There has to be something
else we can do.

32:49.268 --> 32:51.134
Avery, where are you?

32:51.136 --> 32:54.204
(heavy door sliding open)

33:01.446 --> 33:03.447
Danielle.

33:03.449 --> 33:04.748
You remember her?

33:04.750 --> 33:07.184
My former patient?

33:07.186 --> 33:09.553
Mm-hmm, the one
that you didn't give up on.

33:09.555 --> 33:12.055
The one that you devoted
so much time to.

33:12.057 --> 33:14.057
The one that
you chose to help

33:14.059 --> 33:15.759
When you didn't
want to help me.

33:15.761 --> 33:18.662
For that reason,
she had to die.

33:18.664 --> 33:20.764
Oh, you were so convinced

33:20.766 --> 33:22.299
That her abusive
ex-husband killed her,

33:22.301 --> 33:24.601
You even testified
against him.

33:24.603 --> 33:26.103
You helped convict
an innocent man,

33:26.105 --> 33:28.505
And now he is
rotting in jail.

33:28.507 --> 33:30.507
You killed danielle.

33:30.509 --> 33:33.343
It's so much harder
than you would think

33:33.345 --> 33:36.046
To strangle a person.

33:38.149 --> 33:42.319
People find strength
when they're facing death, hmm?

33:44.789 --> 33:46.390
But dr. Chan--

33:46.392 --> 33:48.558
Ooh.

33:48.560 --> 33:50.660
He put up much more of a fight

33:50.662 --> 33:53.230
Than your little friend,
danielle.

33:53.232 --> 33:55.732
What? No response?

33:55.734 --> 33:57.768
(laughs)

33:57.770 --> 34:01.772
You act like
you are so... Emotionless,

34:01.774 --> 34:03.774
But I know the truth.

34:03.776 --> 34:05.809
Yeah, yeah, I knew

34:05.811 --> 34:08.278
That you would transfer
that video

34:08.280 --> 34:11.782
To all of your devices
because of its

34:11.784 --> 34:14.051
Sentimental value.

34:14.786 --> 34:16.787
Your emotions are the reason

34:16.789 --> 34:20.290
That I've been able
to watch you all these years.

34:20.292 --> 34:22.793
Do you understand
what you've done, logan?

34:22.795 --> 34:25.062
(panting)

34:25.797 --> 34:28.432
Do you? Hmm?

34:28.434 --> 34:30.634
Hmm?

34:30.636 --> 34:35.806
I did this for
you, for us.

34:35.808 --> 34:37.774
(ryan coughs)
this is where we began,

34:37.776 --> 34:39.776
And this is where
we're going to end.

34:43.681 --> 34:45.849
(inhales loudly
through his nose)

34:45.851 --> 34:47.417
(exhales though mouth)

34:47.419 --> 34:49.453
It's carbon monoxide poisoning.

34:51.522 --> 34:53.657
(laughing): I bet that
you thought that you

34:53.659 --> 34:55.826
Have to be in, like, oh,
a small, enclosed space,

34:55.828 --> 34:59.229
Like a... A car, right,
for it to kill you.

34:59.231 --> 35:00.831
Uh-uh. Uh-uh.

35:00.833 --> 35:05.135
No, it just takes a little bit
in the air, and you're dead.

35:05.137 --> 35:07.137
You think,
because you outweigh me,

35:07.139 --> 35:09.406
It ensures
that I'll die before you?

35:11.142 --> 35:13.210
But what if I don't?

35:21.819 --> 35:24.254
(grunting)

35:32.130 --> 35:34.631
(coughing)

35:41.205 --> 35:43.273
(phone ringing)

35:44.842 --> 35:47.177
This is elijah mundo.

35:47.179 --> 35:49.346
Ryan (exhales):
It's me.

35:49.348 --> 35:51.381
It's avery.

35:51.383 --> 35:54.284
Four eight two six...

35:54.286 --> 35:55.919
Riverside drive.

35:55.921 --> 35:59.156
It's carbon...

36:00.191 --> 36:01.658
A-avery?

36:01.660 --> 36:03.727
Avery?

36:14.238 --> 36:15.939
It's got a keypad entry.

36:15.941 --> 36:18.208
Elijah, elijah, we got this.

36:32.256 --> 36:33.690
Got it?
One more second.

36:33.692 --> 36:35.292
We're good.

36:36.928 --> 36:38.495
Okay, we're in.

36:38.497 --> 36:40.730
Now, now, go!
Okay, guys, move out.

36:44.302 --> 36:46.203
Avery?

36:47.271 --> 36:49.306
Can you hear me?

36:49.308 --> 36:51.241
Avery,

36:51.243 --> 36:52.342
Can you hear me?

36:52.344 --> 36:53.643
Avery!

36:53.645 --> 36:55.545
<i>Avery?</i>

36:55.547 --> 36:57.647
(groaning)

36:59.450 --> 37:02.485
We were worried about you
for a moment there.

37:02.487 --> 37:03.853
Huh.

37:03.855 --> 37:05.589
Oh, my head is splitting.

37:05.591 --> 37:07.958
(sirens blaring)
how long was I out for?

37:07.960 --> 37:10.493
Just a few minutes.

37:10.495 --> 37:11.962
Logan, did we get him?

37:11.964 --> 37:13.563
Sifter:
No.

37:13.565 --> 37:14.864
You got him, avery.

37:14.866 --> 37:16.933
It's over now.

37:38.624 --> 37:42.993
Man (over radio):
Attention all units
in the vicinity of j street.

37:42.995 --> 37:45.262
Officers requesting
backup and a bus.

37:49.000 --> 37:51.034
Call came in
an hour ago.

37:51.036 --> 37:54.337
Unis are canvassing
the area for witnesses.

37:54.339 --> 37:56.306
Can you confirm
an I.D. On the vic?

37:56.308 --> 37:57.941
Taylor pettis.

37:57.943 --> 37:59.276
Wallet and license

37:59.278 --> 38:00.744
Were in his pocket.

38:00.746 --> 38:02.045
Still had 200 bucks on him.

38:02.047 --> 38:03.546
Not a robbery.

38:03.548 --> 38:05.782
No.

38:05.784 --> 38:08.018
No, someone came here
to kill him.

38:08.020 --> 38:10.353
(camera shutter clicking)

38:14.458 --> 38:16.426
(door opening)

38:16.428 --> 38:18.461
Andrew:
<i>Hi. Come on in, please.</i>

38:18.463 --> 38:20.930
<i>What a surprise. I...</i>

38:20.932 --> 38:24.734
You didn't have to come all the
way out here to check up on me.

38:24.736 --> 38:26.970
Well, no. I-I wanted to...

38:26.972 --> 38:29.406
Tell you I was
sorry in person.

38:29.408 --> 38:31.808
I-I know my team
roughed you up, and...

38:31.810 --> 38:34.377
I just never talk about my past,

38:34.379 --> 38:36.613
So they didn't know who you are.

38:36.615 --> 38:38.782
I...

38:38.784 --> 38:41.318
I'm glad you're safe, avery.

38:42.520 --> 38:44.621
Thanks.

38:44.623 --> 38:45.955
You are okay?

38:45.957 --> 38:46.956
You're not hurt?

38:46.958 --> 38:48.458
Yeah, I'm okay.

38:48.460 --> 38:50.927
Just part of the job. (laughs)

38:50.929 --> 38:54.030
My girl-- still so tough.

38:56.968 --> 39:01.404
I mean, this guy was the one
who hacked your practice?

39:01.406 --> 39:02.839
Yes.

39:02.841 --> 39:04.874
His name was logan reeves.

39:04.876 --> 39:08.345
He knew
that I would always cherish...

39:08.347 --> 39:09.813
(groans softly)

39:09.815 --> 39:12.515
...The videos of the two
of us with hannah,

39:12.517 --> 39:14.484
That I'd always
keep them with me.

39:14.486 --> 39:18.121
He embedded a rat in one
particular video file.

39:18.123 --> 39:22.359
Basically, it allowed him
to live inside my computer.

39:22.361 --> 39:25.662
It was the video of us
with hannah in the park.

39:25.664 --> 39:28.465
The last time
all three of us were together.

39:30.768 --> 39:33.036
Can I see it?

39:33.038 --> 39:35.505
The video?
Do... Do you have it?

39:40.144 --> 39:42.779
(sighs)

39:47.051 --> 39:48.718
Oh, wow.

39:48.720 --> 39:50.787
(sighs)

39:52.390 --> 39:54.891
(laughs)

39:56.427 --> 39:57.761
Oh...

39:57.763 --> 39:59.162
(laughs)

40:02.133 --> 40:03.566
(laughs)

40:07.138 --> 40:09.439
(laughs)

40:13.811 --> 40:15.678
Oh.

40:18.649 --> 40:21.484
(laughs)

40:21.486 --> 40:23.553
Oh.

40:29.860 --> 40:33.163
You know...

40:33.165 --> 40:36.766
I remember
this whole day.

40:36.768 --> 40:38.935
Her chasing those bubbles and...

40:38.937 --> 40:41.204
And that duck that took
her whole piece of bread,

40:41.206 --> 40:44.140
And she followed him into
the water, and-and...

40:44.142 --> 40:47.710
And watching her eyes
watch the sunset, and...

40:49.447 --> 40:52.816
This was a perfect day.

40:52.818 --> 40:56.820
An hour doesn't goes by
where I don't think about her.

40:56.822 --> 40:59.489
(voice breaking):
Where I don't miss her.

40:59.491 --> 41:02.559
Losing hannah was the worst
thing I've ever gone through.

41:04.528 --> 41:08.097
Right up there with losing you.

41:08.099 --> 41:11.634
I am so sorry it
tore us apart.

41:14.572 --> 41:16.072
I am so sorry.

41:16.074 --> 41:17.507
(sighs, sniffles)

41:17.509 --> 41:19.609
Oh, me, too, andrew.

41:19.611 --> 41:21.744
Me, too.

41:26.484 --> 41:29.152
Oh, me, too, andrew.

41:57.681 --> 42:00.517
(rolling thunder)

42:02.119 --> 42:03.853
(sighs)

42:05.189 --> 42:06.689
Francine, what's going on?

42:06.691 --> 42:08.024
What happened?

42:08.026 --> 42:11.094
(crying)

42:12.663 --> 42:14.697
I killed him.

42:14.699 --> 42:16.799
Uh...

42:16.801 --> 42:19.202
I did it, daniel.

42:19.204 --> 42:21.271
(crying)

42:23.541 --> 42:26.042
I killed taylor pettis.

